OL,3,CMeet the celebrity hairdresser who was
OL,4,Cserenaded by Dame Shirley Bassey
OL,6,FA hairdresser from has been reflecting
OL,7,Fon his 60-year career, working with
OL,8,Fcelebrities such as singer Dame
OL,9,FShirley Bassey, Robert Plant from Led
OL,10,FZeppelin and actor Dame Barbara
OL,11,FWindsor.
OL,13,FAdrian Rivett recounts how Dame
OL,14,FShirley, wearing "little fluffy
OL,15,Fslippers and a dressing gown", gave
OL,16,Fhim a front-row seat to her show after
OL,17,Fshe realised he did not have a ticket.
