OL,3,CMeet the celebrity hairdresser who was
OL,4,Cserenaded by Dame Shirley Bassey
OL,6,FHe added: "Then she sang 'Kiss Me,
OL,7,FHoney Honey, Kiss Me' to me and I
OL,8,Fwouldn't get up. She pointed her
OL,9,Ffinger at me and said, 'Adrian, you've
OL,10,Fhad your last chance' so I got up and
OL,11,Fgave her a kiss. Then all the men in
OL,12,Fthe audience came down and gave her a
OL,13,Fkiss as well. It was really special."
OL,15,FAdrian's favourite, however, will
OL,16,Falways be Dame Vera Lynn.
