OL,3,CMeet the celebrity hairdresser who was
OL,4,Cserenaded by Dame Shirley Bassey
OL,6,FHe said: "She was absolutely down to
OL,7,Fearth, something happened because the
OL,8,Flast time I did Vera's hair she called
OL,9,Fout and said, 'Adrian, how is your
OL,10,Fmother?'.
OL,12,F"It was very touching, she had
OL,13,Fremembered that my mother was very
OL,14,Fill. She was a thoughtful lady,
OL,15,Famazing."
OL,17,FDespite being a hairdresser for six
OL,18,Fdecades, Adrian still loves his job
OL,19,Fand says the enjoyment comes from
OL,20,Feveryone who walks through the door.
